casebody.data:
Jacqueline A. CHASSMAN, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
LONGVIEW AT MONTVILLE CONDOMINIUM ASSOCIATION, INC./BOARD OF TRUSTEES, and Taylor Management, Defendants-Respondents. C-359 September Term 2018
081478 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 16, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001660-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
